main event: Two white, clear shaped objects, the size of small clouds, were observed moving rapidly and appearing/disappearing at various points in the sky.
interesting points: The objects were observed by radar distance.
The duration, shape, size, sound, and speed of the objects indicated the possibility of something that could not be conclusively identified.
The objects were initially evaluated as possible aircraft.
The objects moved rapidly, appearing and disappearing at various points in the sky.
The objects stood out against the clear night sky.
